OL,7,FNine people involved in the false
OL,8,Fimprisonment, blackmail and torture of
OL,9,Fthree men at a garage on South
OL,10,FTyneside have been jailed.
OL,12,FThe group lured their victims to a
OL,13,Flock-up off Fowler Street, in South
OL,14,FShields, on 18 September last year,
OL,15,Fbefore holding them prisoners.
OL,17,FThe victims were subjected to severe
OL,18,Fviolence including the use of a
OL,19,Fblowtorch and a spade as the offenders
OL,20,Fdemanded significant amounts of money
OL,21,Fto secure their release.
