OL,7,FThey each required hospital treatment
OL,8,Ffor their injuries.
OL,10,FRaids were carried out across the
OL,11,FNorth East in the weeks that followed
OL,12,Fwith nine arrests made.
OL,14,FSeven defendants pleaded guilty to two
OL,15,Fcounts of false imprisonment and one
OL,16,Fcount of blackmail when appearing at
OL,17,FNewcastle Crown Court in April, while
OL,18,Ftwo other suspects admitted affray in
OL,19,FJune.
