OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe offenders have been sentenced
OL,8,Fthroughout September.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police Detective Inspector
OL,11,FMark Atherton said: "This was a
OL,12,Fterrifying ordeal for the three
OL,13,Fvictims who were subjected to
OL,14,Fsignificant levels of violence.
OL,16,F"It is clear the origins to this
OL,17,Foffence lie in organised criminal
OL,18,Factivity linked to drug dealing and
OL,19,Fthese offenders set about to punish
OL,20,Fand intimidate the victims that day.
