OL,7,F"No matter what was behind the
OL,8,Fdispute, the violence faced by the
OL,9,Fvictims that day was sustained and
OL,10,Fsignificant.
OL,12,F"Violence of any kind will never be
OL,13,Ftolerated and a huge amount of work
OL,14,Ffrom a team of specialist detectives
OL,15,Fworking closely with CPS North East
OL,16,FComplex Casework Unit has culminated
OL,17,Fin the conviction of nine violent
OL,18,Foffenders.
