OL,10,Fjustice process.
OL,12,F"As part of Operation Sentinel, our
OL,13,Fdedicated activity to tackle serious
OL,14,Fand organised crime, we will continue
OL,15,Fto consider every tactic at our
OL,16,Fdisposal to dismantle criminal
OL,17,Fnetworks and bring offenders to
OL,18,Fjustice."
